headline: Morgan Stanley upgrades Zebra Tech on improved demand outlook
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley has upgraded Zebra Technologies Corporation (NASDAQ:ZBRA) to “equal weight” from “underweight” on healthier consumer data, improving retail capital expenditures, and de-risked 2025 estimates.
